04:35.781 --> 04:38.451
<b>I thought we were going straight.</b>

04:38.451 --> 04:40.601
<b>Of course, we've been fooled.</b>

04:40.621 --> 04:42.871
<b>Everyone! The sea coast is this way!</b>

04:42.871 --> 04:44.411
<b>Okay, let's go!</b>

04:45.871 --> 04:47.271
<b>We won't let you go!</b>

04:49.631 --> 04:51.441
<b>Leave them to me!</b>

04:52.671 --> 04:54.971
<b>Memory Filament!</b>

05:02.511 --> 05:04.681
<b>Flashback!</b>

05:08.061 --> 05:10.791
<b>Oh, I've got to go grocery shopping...</b>

05:12.401 --> 05:14.861
<b>Big Brother hit me!</b>

05:14.861 --> 05:16.881
<b>It's time to walk my dog.</b>

05:16.881 --> 05:20.681
<b>My son is missing.
Has anyone seen him?</b>

05:21.491 --> 05:23.011
<b>What's going on?</b>

05:23.011 --> 05:25.891
<b>Anyway, let's go before it's too late!</b>

05:26.461 --> 05:27.721
<b>What's going on?</b>

05:27.721 --> 05:29.971
<b>Memories of the former owners</b>

05:29.971 --> 05:32.561
<b>of those souls that've been 
infused into the Homies...</b>

05:32.561 --> 05:35.391
<b>...are flashing back temporarily.</b>

05:35.391 --> 05:38.981
<b>While they're confused,
they're not under Mama's control!</b>

05:38.981 --> 05:42.321
<b>So Luffy-<i>kun</i> and the others can
get out of the forest now!</b>

05:42.321 --> 05:45.041
<b>I see. Thank you, Pudding-<i>chan</i>!</b>

05:48.691 --> 05:52.411
<b>Why?! Since when were you there, Sanji...</b>

05:52.411 --> 05:53.381
<b><i>...san</i>!</b>

