06:05.071 --> 06:07.391
<b>Your eye is beautiful even when you're mad...</b>

06:11.541 --> 06:13.111
<b>Are you okay, Pudding?</b>

06:13.651 --> 06:17.731
<b>I-I'm fine... D-D-Don't mess with me!</b>

06:17.731 --> 06:21.311
<b>O-Or I'll kill you, Sanji...</b>

06:21.311 --> 06:22.871
<b><i>...san</i>!</b>

06:22.871 --> 06:25.481
<b>Oh! It's the end of the forest!</b>

06:25.481 --> 06:28.791
<b>All right! Let's go straight to Cacao Island!</b>

06:35.071 --> 06:36.961
<b>Brook! Chopper!</b>

06:36.961 --> 06:39.091
<b>Is that your ship?</b>

06:39.371 --> 06:41.511
<b>Yeah, it's getting attacked.</b>

06:41.951 --> 06:43.911
<b>I guess they were ambushed...</b>

06:44.531 --> 06:46.681
<b>Oh, no! Our big brothers are there!</b>

06:49.451 --> 06:52.581
<b>Our brothers are attacking 
Sanji-<i>san</i>'s friends...</b>

06:53.541 --> 06:55.711
<b>Hmph! Your friends are dead!</b>

06:55.711 --> 06:59.521
<b>That will teach ya!
They're no match for my brothers!</b>

06:59.521 --> 07:03.241
<b>Your friends will be swallowed by the sea!</b>

07:04.721 --> 07:06.971
<b>What are you saying, Pudding?!</b>

07:06.971 --> 07:11.141
<b>Oh, no! That's not what I meant to say!</b>

07:12.271 --> 07:15.261
<b>What do you wanna do?
Go back to the ship?</b>

07:16.941 --> 07:20.211
<b>No, I'll come along with Pudding-<i>chan</i>.</b>

07:20.211 --> 07:21.261
<b>What?</b>

07:22.821 --> 07:26.301
<b>Are you sure?
