07:26.291 --> 07:29.221
<b>Yeah, we don't need to worry about them.</b>

07:30.121 --> 07:33.461
<b>Instead, let's get started...</b>

07:35.581 --> 07:40.371
<b>...on the cake that can make Big Mom unconscious
