09:34.201 --> 09:37.471
<b>Who are you gonna apologize to? Lick.</b>

09:37.471 --> 09:40.101
<b>You saw the lightning earlier, right?</b>

09:40.711 --> 09:43.191
<b>That was pretty intense.</b>

09:43.731 --> 09:46.641
<b>It shows how mad Mama is.</b>

09:46.641 --> 09:50.811
<b>I bet there aren't even bones left of
Straw Hat and the others.</b>

09:50.811 --> 09:54.081
<b>No one will return to this ship.</b>

09:57.771 --> 10:01.831
<b>I'm saying I'm going to
show some mercy on you.</b>

10:01.831 --> 10:07.541
<b>No matter how much you try,
