10:07.541 --> 10:11.221
<b>And you guys will use up all of your energy
eventually.</b>

10:12.021 --> 10:18.171
<b>If you submit right here, right now,
I'll at least spare your life...</b>

10:18.171 --> 10:20.521
<b>Just let it go already.</b>

10:22.291 --> 10:24.731
<b>What a useless conversation.</b>

10:25.691 --> 10:30.071
<b>We got sick and tired of answering to
