10:31.801 --> 10:34.361
<b>I just need you to get off of the ship.</b>

10:34.361 --> 10:37.241
<b>The Sunny is ours!</b>

10:38.981 --> 10:41.961
<b>Do you really wanna fight me?</b>

10:55.541 --> 10:57.141
<b>I see...</b>

10:57.791 --> 11:02.301
<b>Seems like you really 
