11:02.301 --> 11:03.931
<b>All right.</b>

11:03.931 --> 11:07.141
<b>I'll kill you with my own hands.</b>

11:07.141 --> 11:09.051
<b>Lick.</b>

11:18.141 --> 11:20.541
<b>Cake...</b>

11:21.681 --> 11:23.621
