12:27.811 --> 12:30.271
<b>Yes, I know...</b>

12:30.651 --> 12:35.271
<b>But those were so delicious...
Those thundercloud eggs.</b>

12:35.261 --> 12:36.061
<b>Huh?!</b>

12:36.291 --> 12:41.661
<b>Hey, do you really understand?!
Mama's orders are absolute!</b>

12:41.661 --> 12:43.701
