13:11.361 --> 13:14.151
<b>Everyone, be careful!
Another one's coming!</b>

13:23.051 --> 13:25.271
<b>Cake!</b>

13:26.481 --> 13:27.441
<b>Duck!</b>

13:30.441 --> 13:31.671
<b>Mama!</b>

13:39.781 --> 13:42.431
