15:41.631 --> 15:45.341
<b>Don't worry... I can still fight...</b>

15:47.781 --> 15:52.481
<b>You've cut down quite a lot of our troops...</b>

15:52.481 --> 15:56.151
<b>We'll bring you guys down
and take back the Sunny!</b>

15:56.831 --> 16:01.491
<b>You're so naive...
I'll make you face reality.</b>

16:09.681 --> 16:11.071
<b>Huh? What the...</b>

16:11.071 --> 16:12.121
<b>My leg...</b>

16:14.101 --> 16:16.421
<b>Damn! I can't move!</b>

16:16.921 --> 16:17.841
<b>Chopper-<i>san</i>!</b>

16:21.571 --> 16:22.941
