16:25.471 --> 16:27.011
<b>You fools...</b>

16:27.011 --> 16:32.561
<b>Those candies will slowly 
seep into your bodies.</b>

16:37.541 --> 16:41.461
<b>It's no use.
You won't be able to move from there...</b>

16:45.221 --> 16:46.631
<b>Chopper-<i>san</i>!</b>

16:48.161 --> 16:50.651
<b>Don't panic, don't panic.</b>

16:50.651 --> 16:52.081
<b>Man...</b>

16:52.711 --> 16:59.241
<b>What kind of positive thinking did you have
to believe you could take the ship back?</b>

16:59.241 --> 17:02.871
<b>In order to catch you guys,</b>

17:02.871 --> 17:06.961
